@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Incident Reasoning Agent End to End Flow

actor Reporter
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Incident Reasoning Agent" as Agent
participant "Log Reader" as Logs
participant "Hypothesis Engine" as Reasoner
participant "Ticket Store" as Ticket
participant "Notification Service" as Notify
participant "Engineering Team" as Team

Reporter -> UI: Submit incident report and attachments
UI -> Agent: Forward incident payload
Agent -> Logs: Retrieve relevant log signals
Logs --> Agent: Return observable technical evidence
Agent -> Reasoner: Generate structured hypotheses
Reasoner --> Agent: Summary causes confidence next steps
Agent -> Ticket: Create enriched incident ticket
Ticket --> Agent: Ticket created
Agent -> Notify: Notify engineering team
Notify -> Team: Send structured diagnostic summary
Team --> Ticket: Mark issue resolved
Ticket -> Notify: Resolution event
Notify -> Reporter: Send resolution update
@enduml
